HARD TO FIND 2 BRS WITH 1 1/2 BATHS PLUS OUTDOOR KITCHEN. Fifth Wheel - 3 SLIDEOUTS. Sleeps 8. Rockwood 8301WS More pictures available.

1 ¬Ω Bathrooms. Amazing Outdoor kitchen. 2 Entrances. Triple Slideouts. Bunk Room. High Ceilings. Large awning. Outdoor shower. Pass through basement storage. Fireplace. 2 TVs, with room for another in the main bedroom and one outside. Exterior speakers. Extra Large Dinette. Sleeps 8. 

OUTDOOR KITCHEN includes refrigerator, sink, 2 burner gas range plus storage.  Great place to plug in your coffee maker and toaster. The pull up door provides cover for sun and/or rain. We set up a Blackstone right next to the outdoor kitchen it and do most of the cooking outside.

VERY CLEAN AND TASTEFUL INTERIOR. 

2017 Forest River RV Rockwood Signature ULTRA LITE 8301WS, Forest River Rockwood Signature Ultra Lite fifth wheel 8301WS highlights:- Triple Slide Outs- Rear Bunk Room- Bath and a Half- Two Entry Doors- Outdoor Kitchen. Enjoy the convenience of a power awning complemented by LED lights. Seamless one-piece roof that adds durability and style. Basement storage. Reese revolution hitch.
